data.description: Welcome to this unique real estate opportunity! Nestled on a R-2 lot Live in one and rent out the other.. This property presents an excellent investment potential as a multi-unit dwelling.The first residence, conveniently located at the front of the property, is a well-appointed 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home.,This dwelling provides a comfortable and inviting living space, making it an ideal choice for occupants.Adding to the property's charm, the second home is discreetly accessed through the alley, ensuring privacy for both units. This secondary dwelling is a studio with 1 bathroom, Excitingly, this property also holds potential for expansion. Prospective buyers may explore the possibility of constructing two additional units on the premises, offering an enticing opportunity for increased rental income or multifamily living. However, it is crucial for new buyers to conduct thorough due diligence and verify the feasibility of such expansion plans with the city authorities.The neighborhood is known for its convenient location, proximity to amenities, Whether you're an investor seeking to maximize rental income or a homeowner looking for a property with supplementary rental income.
